13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 150.12A-1,
15 is amended to read as follows:
16 Section 150.12A-1. A. The Oklahoma State Bureau of
17 Investigation shall coordinate with the United States Attorney's
18 Office and the United States Department of Justice to obtain federal
19 funding by January 1, 2022, to coordinate efforts and gather data to
20 address the issue of missing and murdered indigenous persons in the
21 State of Oklahoma. The Bureau shall seek and apply for any
22 applicable federal grants and may coordinate with private entities
23 to obtain funding or fulfill grant requirements.
24
